    "description": "We at Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions are looking for an experienced Radiologist based out of Visakhapatnam. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions:\nIpca Laboratories Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions!",
